<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>130</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Niongoze, Bwana Mungu,
 Ni msafiri chini;
 Ni mnyonge, nguvu sina:
 Nishike mkononi;
 U mkate wa Mbinguni,
 nilishe siku zote.

[V2]
 Kijito cha maji mema,
 Kitokacho mwambani,
 Nguzo yako, moto, wingu,
 Yaongoza jangwani;
 Niokoe mwenye nguvu;
 Nguvu zangu na ngao.

[V3]
 Nikikaribia kufa,
 Sichi neno lolote,
 Wewe kifo umeshinda
 Zinawe nguvu zote,
 Tutaimba sifa zako,
 Kwako juu milele.</lyrics>
<title>Niongoze, Bwana Mungu TZR130</title>
</song>